fields.name: NoSpermText_0
fields.fieldText:
It looks like we don't have a egg cohort associated with this embryo. You will need to specify the source for ANZARD.


Cycle Type 1 should be selected when the embryo was created utilising the patients own eggs.


Cycle Type 2 should be selected when the embryo was created utilising the partner's eggs.


Cycle Type 4 should be selected when the embryo was created utilising a donor's eggs.


Cycle Type 5 should be selected when the embryo has been donated from outside the intending parents.
